  "text": "We also compared the morphological characteristics of color and scutellation of the specimens collected with other representatives of the genus These new records of the adult male and juvenile male from Hidalgo, represent a straight-line range extension of 24 km and 25 km, respectively, from the nearest locations, 16.09 km southwest of Villa Juárez, Xicotepec de Juárez, Puebla, and 83.6 km and 82.5 km, respectively, from the type locality, 3.5 km west of Xocoyolo, Municipality of Cuetzalan, Puebla, Mexico [CITATION_1] ; Figure 2 ).",
